    <p>The deals are avail­able from Mon­days to Thurs­days at Hard Rock Cafe Sin­ga­pore: “Starters” on Mon­days (ex­clud­ing jumbo combo), “Iconic Steak Burg­ers” on Tues­days, “Sig­na­ture Cock­tails” on Wed­nes­days and “Deca­dent Desserts” on Thurs­days. The pro­mo­tion ap­plies only for dine-in.</p>
    <p>WHERE: Hard Rock Cafe Sin­ga­pore, 02-01 HPL House, 50 Cus­ca­den Road</p>
    <p>MRT: Or­chard WHEN: Till Sept 30, 11.30am - 9.30pm daily PRICE: From $18.95 for starters TEL: 6235-5232 INFO: www.face­book.com/hardrock­cafesin­ga­pore</p>


